high_descs: Turn around and walk to the round table.
Pick up the dirty plate from the table.
Turn left and walk to the front of the sink.
Clean the dirty plate with clean water in the sink.
Turn right and move to the right of the sink.
Place the clean dish to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Clean the dirty plate on the table using the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the door, then turn left and walk over to the wooden table.
Pick up the dirty plate off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the dirty plate in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean plate.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn around.
Put the clean plate on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean grey plate on the counter.

high_descs: go to the round dining table
pick up the pie plate from the table
take the plate to the sink, wash it and remove
take a few steps to your left
put the plate on the right side of the sink on the counter
anns.task_desc: take the dirty pie plate from the table, wash it in the sink, then put it on the counter.
